episode_summary: In this episode, Fee Gentry discusses strategies for REALTORS to future-proof their business by leveraging strategic partnerships and diversifying income streams. She emphasizes the importance of maintaining a positive mindset and adapting to industry changes, offering actionable insights on how agents can maximize their earnings beyond traditional commissions.
